            "text": ", the answer seems to be a resounding “yes.” The Blue Oval has taken 125,000 orders, despite a series of delays in launching the all-new off-roader with a nostalgic badge. However, Ford says it plans to build about 80,000 Broncos in 2021 and 160,000 in 2022. In other words, you might have to wait until next year ",
